{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"197794be-e0a0-49f7-9cb2-0dca288ea76a","content":"No workflow files found locally, so here's general guidance on switching to NuGet trusted publishing (OIDC):\n\n## Changes Needed\n\n**1. On nuget.org** — Configure a trusted publisher:\n- Go to your package → Manage → Publishing → Add Trusted Publisher\n- Set the GitHub repo owner, repo name, workflow filename, and (optionally) environment\n\n**2. In your workflow** — Add OIDC permissions and replace the `dotnet nuget push` auth:\n\n```yaml\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write   # Required for OIDC\n      contents: read\n    # Optional: tie to a GitHub environment for extra protection\n    # environment: nuget-publish\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4\n        with:\n          dotnet-version: '8.x'\n\n      - run: dotnet pack -c Release\n\n      - name: Push to NuGet\n        uses: dotnet/push-nuget@v1   # Official trusted-publish action\n        with:\n          source: https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n**3. Remove** the `secrets.NUGET_API_KEY` reference and the secret itself from your repo settings once verified.\n\n### Key differences from API-key auth:\n| Before | After |\n|--------|-------|\n| `--api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }}` | No key needed — OIDC token is exchanged automatically |\n| No special permissions block | `permissions: id-token: write` required |\n| Secret rotation burden | No secrets to manage |\n\nIf the official `dotnet/push-nuget` action isn't available yet for your setup, you can use `dotnet nuget push` with the `--api-key` replaced by a short-lived token obtained via the `azure/login` or a custom OIDC step — but the action above is the simplest path.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"2f170fde-ef80-4fd4-8e0c-b7bdc1a86966","outputTokens":479,"requestId":"0403:1BDA61:9A636F:B47645:69F3FB04"},"id":"394417dc-ca02-4943-811d-1333cc0cd5e7","timestamp":"2026-05-01T01:00:00.574Z","parentId":"d0471cd8-56ab-4076-8eb8-f454e89758f2"}
